<英文法規名稱>Regulations on the Use of Captions in Shopping Channels of Satellite Broadcasting Businesses</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>衛星廣播電視購物頻道插播式字幕管理辦法</中文法規名稱>
<法規網址>https://law.moj.gov.tw/Eng/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?pcode=P0050046</法規網址>
<最新英文異動日期>20161004</最新英文異動日期>
<廢止註記>
</廢止註記>
<附件 />
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.5 Articles promulgated in full by National Communications Commission on October 4, 2016. Ref：Tong-Chuan-Nei-Rong No.10548027660]]></沿革內容>
<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These regulations are enacted in accordance with the provisions of Paragraph 37, Article 2 of the Satellite Broadcasting Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The term “captions” in these regulations refers to text and graphics appearing on the screen that have been edited and compiled and are not part of the original contents being broadcasted.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The use of captions shall not interfere with the viewing of programs by the public; broadcasters shall consider the interests of the audience when determining how and when to use captions.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Broadcasters shall provide captions of the consumer complaint procedure on the bottom of the TV screen, and shall make them clear, prominent, and identifiable.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These regulations shall come into force as of the date of promulgation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
